{
  "stem": "2833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one day, we got a order to send 1,000 women into an area in Czechoslovakia to plant trees-- a wood-- woods.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was in charge of this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so I also put the group together for myself with all my friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were taken by train to the little town, which I had known since I was a small child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that's why I wanted to go, because my family had some textile factories there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I had gone on vacation in summer very often there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I know-- knew the kids I played with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I knew a lot of the workers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so I figured, if I go, I might get some-- somebody who I know who would-- who I could trust.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And sure enough, at the railroad station, there was an old man who worked for the family all his life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he knew me since I was riding on his shoulder as a little girl.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he was very smart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they had trucks they had to put our knapsacks and bedding, which we had to take along on the truck and drive it up on the mountain.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So he came to me, asked me what number group I have, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And by the time we came to work, we were only guarded by Czech forester, and only had Czech gendarmes in the little house that we lived in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were 12 in my group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So it was much, much easier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And sure enough, we got there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And after two days, somebody came and-- hiding in the wood-- and motioned me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I went there, and he said, look in the trees.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
